snippet.title: Warhammer: Vermintide 2 - Official Karak Azgaraz Free Update Trailer
snippet.description: Wtach the trailer to see what to expect with Warhammer: Vermintide 2's upcoming Karak Azgaraz free new content update, featuring three newly remastered adventure maps from the DLC of the first Vermintide game.
